### Create a deal
# Use with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client
# Requires the API to be running: npm run dev -w @repo/api

POST http://localhost:3000/deals
Content-Type: application/json
x-tenant-id: your-tenant-uuid-here

{
  "title": "123 Main St — Buyer Representation",
  "contactName": "Jane Smith",
  "contactEmail": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "value": "425000.00",
  "stage": "qualified"
}

### Get all deals for a tenant

GET http://localhost:3000/deals
x-tenant-id: your-tenant-uuid-here

### Health check

GET http://localhost:3000/health
